{"tid":986082,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打睇過2009年港產片《死神傻了》？","createTime":"2019-01-18T07:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T08:34:46.000Z","uid":210794,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a16cda54afffa06f364050470619ddfda337c6a0","tid":986082,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:20:34.000Z","msg":"悶悶哋上網搵咗呢套舊戲，睇完覺得輕鬆cult片嚟講算係咁，當然唔會話好好睇但起碼題材幾特別，睇嚟笑吓都okay，又有啲黑色幽默元素⋯⋯<br />\n（仲有Kay BB 娜姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但之後上網上想睇吓啲人點評，點知好似冇乜人知有呢套戲，舊登都得一個post仲要個個踩到一文不值⋯⋯<br />\n有少少覺得如果套戲係喺呢一兩年上嘅話評價未必會以前咁差⋯⋯<br />\n（利申唔係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係睇完戲想同人傾吓）"},{"pid":"3cd8a300120ed8573ecc5c4099cf383d488ce400","tid":986082,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c067b74253b404b153856e19fde8a1f07ee46d7","tid":986082,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cd8a300120ed8573ecc5c4099cf383d488ce400","tid":986082,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:31:35.000Z","msg":"邱禮濤年年都有幾套戲開使搵我做打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e9413503386dd06dbc1a0cc22b2a1e8f525edc","tid":986082,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"幾好笑下"},{"pid":"600057ccb2687ae6061e8ec767aaf8718ce137a4","tid":986082,"uid":171107,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"果時雞容打手多 淫kay彈起佢地唔抵得 係要將淫kay踩到好似雞容咁既票房毒藥"},{"pid":"758854d861137c39a9661a2e6d4564874428c9be","tid":986082,"uid":210794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"600057ccb2687ae6061e8ec767aaf8718ce137a4","tid":986082,"uid":171107,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"果時雞容打手多 淫kay彈起佢地唔抵得 係要